metadata.description:
West Africa Street Food Suya
Suya is probably the most popular streets food in west Africa sold on mostly every corners and beyond. It is skewered meat that is roasted and served with spices which give it a unique aroma and taste. It is believed to be originated with the Hausa people in Northern Nigeria.

Shot: 
Kaduna Nigeria, Dec 2018
